$Id$
================
XMLZEN CHANGELOG
================
http://xmlzen.googlecode.com

Changes in version 0.2.0 (2010-08-?)
* Fixed a bug which prevented getting attribute values in some cases
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=11
* Added a possibility to set some defaults for XmlBuilder
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=10
* Added XmlBuilderOutput interface with String and OutputStream implementations
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=8
* XmlBuilder builds formatted XML with declaration (if charset is provided)
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=9
* File support in XmlBuilder (through XmlBuilderStreamOutput) and XmlSlicer
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=7

Changes in version 0.1.1 (2009-10-03)
* Added possibility to build formatted XML.
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=1
* XmlBuilder.toString() no longer closes all tags. toString(true) does.
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=2
* Added XmlSlicer.value() method that returns value of first tag of current XML.
  http://code.google.com/p/xmlzen/issues/detail?id=3    

Changes in version 0.1.0 (2009-09-27)
-------------------------------------
* Initial release